		<div id="comment_body_64185853"><p><div class="quote"><p>Is this the same Harvard that holds almost $50 BILLION dollars in their endowment?</p></div><p>No, this is Dana Farber, a large teaching hospital that is institutionally independent from Harvard College, but is affiliated with (i.e. trains students from) Harvard Medical School -- as are about eight other major Boston area hospitals.  It's roughly analogous to your local vocational high school having an arrangment with some local car repair shops to help train students and provide internships.</p></div>
	</div>

